00:00:00.630 --> 00:00:04.200
We mentioned a few paid options and
finished up the paid marketing portion

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.820
of the lesson with some of the basics of
paid social media marketing channels.

00:00:08.820 --> 00:00:12.370
However, social media is integrated so
well into our lives

00:00:12.370 --> 00:00:17.070
that there are many ways to leverage
social media for your business for free.

00:00:17.070 --> 00:00:20.500
The idea is use social
platforms to encourage people

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.920
to spread the word about your
app within their circles.

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:26.720
The first step in doing this is
to engage the community online

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:28.570
using social platforms.

00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:31.840
This is where we are going to start
talking about free marketing methods for

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:33.240
your business.

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:36.030
After we talk about the free social
communities to help with customer

00:00:36.030 --> 00:00:38.660
acquisition, we're going to
look into inbound marketing.

